reviewText: excellent childrens show, teaches many things and the characters are wonderful.. I bought his for my grandchild, and he loves it.

Great dvd. Brought it for my granddaughter and I must say she loves it and watches it everyday since she got it. My kids use to watch this and I was surprise to se it is still available. I must purchase others. They are not only fun but educational.
